      <hedline>
        <hl1>For Real Road Warriors</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>James W Hamilton letter on popularity of Hummer asks if we can look forward to civilian versions of armored personnel carriers (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>With the popularity and commercial success of the General Motors Hummer (front page, Aug. 6), can we look forward to civilian versions of the Bradley armored personnel carrier and the M1-A1 Abrams tank?</p>
        <p>JAMES W. HAMILTON  Santa Fe, N.M., Aug. 7, 2000</p>
      </block>
